%F A029270 a(n) = floor((n^3+48*n^2+684*n+6440)/8640 - (n mod 2)*(n^2+29*n)/960 - ((2*n^2+n) mod 3)*n/36 + ((n^2+n+2) mod 4)*n/96 - (n mod 3)/3 + ((n+3) mod 4)/8). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Mar 25 2026
